  "html": "<div class=\"fr-view\"><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">Day 56 - Kanji Practice</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">Please download today&#39;s kanji practice here:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\"><a class=\"fr-file\" href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/thinkific/file_uploads/259518/attachments/a23/599/900/Kanji_Practice_Day_56.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Kanji Practice Day 56.pdf</a></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">Practising writing kanji every day is a very important exercise to help you learn quickly. If you have any questions you can always ask other students and teachers in the community&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/communities/Q29tbXVuaXR5LTM1MzQ=\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">here</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">Refer back to the </span><a href=\"https://japaneseonline.gogonihon.com/manage/courses/731527/contents/18335350\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">Week 12 - Kanji lesson</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\"> to watch how to do the correct stroke order for the <span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">高,</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">小</span> &amp; <span style=\"color: rgb(91, 91, 91);\">新</span> kanji. <br></span></p></div>",
